## Pull Request Overview

This PR adds support for counting packages managed by the KISS package ma=
nager, a Linux package manager. The implementation follows the establishe=
d pattern used by other package managers in the codebase.

Key changes:
- Adds KISS package counting functionality with dedicated detection funct=
ion
- Integrates KISS support into the existing package management framework
- Updates documentation to reflect the new package manager support

